        </h2>
        <div class="mt-6 text-gray-500 space-y-6 text-lg">
          <p>
            The customer support space has normally been occupied with boring enterprisey tools, focussed on ticket numbers, the complex routing of requests to different teams and not a whole lot of focus on people.
          </p>
          <p>
            Live chat has disrupted the space, but brought with it a whole new host of challenges and expectations. Don’t get us wrong, tools like intercom are great, if you have the manpower to answer messages instantly, worldwide.
